Class CampList

All Implemented Interfaces:

CampDetails
public class CampList extends RepositoryList<Camp> implements IFilterableByID<Camp>, IFilterableByDateRange<Camp>, IFilterableBySchool<Camp>, IFilterableByVisibility<Camp>, ISortableByEndDate<Camp>, ISortableByID<Camp>, ISortableByLocation<Camp>, ISortableByName<Camp>, ISortableByRegistrationCloseDate<Camp>, ISortableByStartingDate<Camp>, IFilterableByAttendee<Camp>, IFilterableByCampCommittee<Camp>, IFilterableByStudent<Camp>
Represents a list of camps, providing functionality for filtering and sorting camps based on various criteria. This class extends RepositoryList and implements several interfaces for filtering and sorting.
